@startuml Sequence Diagram
actor User
participant LoginPage
participant AuthContext
participant APIClient
participant Backend
database Database

User -> LoginPage: Enter email & password
User -> LoginPage: Click "Access Watchlist"

LoginPage -> AuthContext: login(password) // Base64 encoded
AuthContext -> APIClient: POST /auth/login
APIClient -> Backend: Request Authentication

Backend -> Database: Find User by Email
Database --> Backend: User data (hashed password)

Backend -> Backend: Validate Password
alt Success
  Backend -> Backend: Generate JWT Token
  Backend --> APIClient: { access_token: "...", token_type: "bearer" }
  APIClient --> AuthContext: Response
  AuthContext -> AuthContext: Save token to localStorage
  AuthContext -> AuthContext: Set isAuthenticated = true
  LoginPage -> LoginPage: navigate("/home")
else Failure
  Backend --> APIClient: 401 Unauthorized
  APIClient --> AuthContext: Error
  AuthContext --> LoginPage: Display Error Message
end
@enduml
